<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiun zie thusim maktak mai hi,
 Khatvei mi mang I na hiu;
 Mahleh Van Lal lopi hung kum chun,
 Man sim guolloh in ei tan.

[V2]
 I henkawl buh kuo a ei sut?
 Bang A bawl em?
 Tu'n khawia um?
 I sikgen in Vanah A um.

[V3]
 2. Angel I mun luoh theih ding umlo,
 A chungnung pen hilele;
 Mi nuolsuot Kross a khetdena um,
 Pathien thumte laka khat.
 3. Zie thusim maktak hi chieh zel hen,
 Lung leh lei tin chawktho hen;
 I thiempu Lal, I sikgen a pang,
 Amin chu Krista Isu.

[V4]
 4. Hukdampa di'n na kipum piek dem?
 Lungthim niemin na khu'n dem?
 A lungsiet hedi'n nangle hungin,
 Tun nang hun hukdam ina.</lyrics>
<title>WHAT DID HE DO</title>
<hymn_number>75</hymn_number>
</song>